%h3 Create spread

%h4 POST /album/\#{album.permalink}/spreads.json OR /album/\#{album.permalink}/spreads.xml

%h5 Request

%p Temporarily we recommend that you submit a spread create request as a POST of name-value pairs:

%pre
  %code
    spread[image] = \#{Filedata}

%br

%h5 Response

%pre
  %code Status: 201 Created

%br

%h3 Destroy spread

%p
  %b *** IMPORTANT: To replace an existing spread, rather than deleting, just create a spread with the same filename ***

%h4
  DELETE /album/\#{album.permalink}/spreads/\#{spread.id}.json OR
  %br
  \/album/\#{album.permalink}/spreads/\#{spread.id}.xml

%h5 Response

%pre
  %code Status: 200 OK
